Servo Controller
================

ServoController is a simple test application for servo control using
Atmel AVR microcontrollers and a custom serial protocol. For details
on the serial protocol, see the below section.

Building the Application
------------------------

You'll need the following dependencies:

* Qt >= 4.0
* Serial port or USB-to-serial adapter
* ServoController hardware device

### Compile

	user@host:~/ServoController# make
	user@host:~/ServoController# make install

### Run

	user@host:~# ServoController

